ights-online", "storyline": "Remote Knights Online is a faction based openworld multiplayer action RPG with survival elements.You control your avatar from a freely adjustable 3rd person to 1st person perspective in a seamless handcrafted 3D world.\nMain goal of the game is to survive and lead your faction to victory in a combination of PvE and PvP.\nThe world changes dynamically according to the behavior of the players,\nYou can play it in singleplayer, multiplayer or in self-hosted mode with custom ruleset.\n\nPlayers can join one of two factions in order to gain dominion over Vall Tir in atmospheric multiplayer/singleplayer battles.Each fraction has its own history, culture and religion, which is reflected in the style of play, music and general ambience.\nPlay your way up in their ranks with friends or alone, unlock new skins, achievements, and more..\nEvery time you spawn, you play a new life, because by death you lose all items and the ingame level progression.\nBut if you manage to recover your treasure before an opponent has done it, you lose nothing.\nGeneral account level, unlocked content, achievements, etc. should be spared from death.", "summary": "A faction-based openworld action RPG with survival elements. Playable in multiplayer, singleplayer and self-hosted mode with custom ruleset. Can you survive the rough world of Vall Tir?", "themes": [{"id": 1, "name": "Action"}, {"id": 17, "name": "Fantasy"}, {"id": 21, "name": "Survival"}, {"id": 38, "name": "Open world"}], "url": "https://www.igdb.com/games/remote-knights-online", "videos": [{"id": 56004, "name": "Trailer", "video_id": "pyv1viyjcyc", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pyv1viyjcyc", "title": "Remote Knights Online Pre-Alpha Gameplay Trailer", "thumb": "https://i.ytimg.com/vi/pyv1viyjcyc/maxresdefault.jpg"}]}